---
title: Hellmann's® Sesame Thai Cashew Chicken with Lime-Coconut Rice
description: Hellmann's® Sesame Thai Dressing makes your weeknight dinner a cinch to pull off! This sauce hero helps our cashew chicken stir-fry come together in no time. You'll pile it up on fluffy lime-coconut rice and top it off with fresh cilantro and crunchy toasted cashews to create fuss-free flavour fun!
